OL,7,FVulnerable close contacts of people
OL,8,Fwith invasive Strep A infections will
OL,9,Fbe given antibiotics in a bid to
OL,10,Fcontain rising cases of the disease,
OL,11,Fthe UK Health Security Agency has
OL,12,Fannounced.
OL,14,FWomen in their 37th week of pregnancy
OL,15,For later, new mothers and their babies,
OL,16,Fpeople aged over 75, and those who have
OL,17,Fhad chickenpox in the previous week
OL,18,Fwill be given the medicine if they have
OL,19,Fcome into close contact with invasive
OL,20,FStrep A (iGAS) patients, even if they
OL,21,Fdo not have symptoms.
